95
00:05:38,790 --> 00:05:43,360
(Istana Chao Sheng)

96
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:56,230
Dewa Agung,

97
00:05:56,600 --> 00:05:57,600
benar awak nak...

98
00:05:57,600 --> 00:05:58,600
Awak tak perlu cakap lagi.

99
00:05:58,880 --> 00:05:59,790
Saya dah buat keputusan.

100
00:06:00,830 --> 00:06:02,160
Ini satu-satunya cara yang ada.

101
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:03,920
Namun, kita boleh beritahu
Dewa Agung Zhi Yang

102
