semua makhluk hidup,

105
00:06:11,200 --> 00:06:13,000
Shang Gu dan beribu-ribu nyawa.

106
00:06:13,830 --> 00:06:15,440
Awak rasa, siapa yang
akan mereka sokong?

107
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:41,670
Kenapa?

108
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:43,550
Dewi Salji baru siap memperalat saya,

109
00:06:44,440 --> 00:06:46,480
