110
00:06:47,110 --> 00:06:48,480
Dewi Salji, usah cemas.

111
00:06:48,790 --> 00:06:50,350
Sekarang, awak
bakal bertukar jadi iblis.

112
00:06:50,350 --> 00:06:51,200
Secara lebih tepatnya,

113
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:55,350
