114
00:06:57,440 --> 00:06:58,390
Mengarut!

115
00:06:59,270 --> 00:07:00,350
Saya merupakan Dewi Salji,

116
00:07:01,070 --> 00:07:02,270
tak mungkin saya ahli Puak Iblis?

117
00:07:04,160 --> 00:07:05,040
Ya atau tidak,

118
00:07:05,830 --> 00:07:07,640
Dewi Salji ada masa untuk fikirkannya.

119
00:07:08,110 --> 00:07:11,510
Namun, jangan terlupa
perkara yang awak janjikan.

120
00:07:13,760 --> 00:07:15,200
Dalam upacara perwarisan esok,

121
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:17,440
awak merupakan mata Iblis Agung.

122
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:19,390
Kami dah bantu awak
untuk kembali ke Alam Dewa,

123
00:07:20,390 --> 00:07:23,760
permintaan kecil ini pasti tak melampau.

124
00:07:48,880 --> 00:07:49,790
Wu Huan!

125
00:07:50,110 --> 00:07:50,950
Tuk.

126
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:55,920
Dah lama saya tak jumpa tuk.

127
00:07:56,390 --> 00:07:57,550
Adakah tuk sihat?

128
00:07:58,040 --> 00:07:59,160
Semuanya baik.

129
00:07:59,950 --> 00:08:00,880
Tuk, sila masuk.

130
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:01,640
Baiklah.

131
00:08:05,880 --> 00:08:06,440
Wu Huan!

132
00:08:11,880 --> 00:08:13,440
Sekarang, Wu Huan amat bermegah.

133
00:08:13,760 --> 00:08:16,230
Dia dah jauh berbeza daripada waktunya
dalam puak ribuan tahun lalu.

134
00:08:16,880 --> 00:08:18,230
Dia hanya orang keji yang berjaya.

135
00:08:18,640 --> 00:08:20,070
Selepas Raja Burung mencapai nirwana
dan kembali semula,

136
00:08:20,230 --> 00:08:22,670
tak mungkin ada kedudukannya
di Istana Chao Sheng lagi.

137
00:08:22,880 --> 00:08:23,720
Betul.

138
00:08:30,070 --> 00:08:32,760
Wu Huan, tolong saya salin pakaian.

139
00:08:36,480 --> 00:08:37,390
Wu Huan.

140
00:08:49,110 --> 00:08:51,710
Kenapa awak berada di sini?

141
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:53,150
Sekarang dah lewat,

142
00:08:53,470 --> 00:08:54,550
tapi saya tak jumpa awak
di mana-mana pun.

143
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:55,790
Saya pun datang ke istana
untuk jumpa awak.

144
00:08:56,350 --> 00:08:57,400
Wu Huan kata awak tak nak bangun,

145
